    "name": "霓虹巅峰：超越极限",
    "steam_appid": 3039250,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;2124年，地球。秩序已然破碎，万象皆非所见，但在赛道上，真相终将显现……”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎来到霓虹巅峰</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2124 年，人类建立的城市早已湮灭，智能生命主宰世界，钢筋水泥铸成的丛林里只剩最后一条铁律：强者生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《霓虹巅峰：超越极限》是一款超高速的街机风格赛车游戏。人类精英、AI智械和改造人对决于赛道之上。紧绷神经，精准漂移，在时速200英里的狂飙中为荣耀而战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/2999c89cd1611815418e132991cd453b.poster.avif?t=1760645571\" width=620 height=313 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/2999c89cd1611815418e132991cd453b.webm?t=1760645571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>武装你的座驾</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从各具风格、专为竞速打造的众多赛车和摩托中挑选座驾。用比赛奖金来为爱车改装配置、提升性能，换上最拉风的涂装。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/ca8a79f05ddc2b131727d551023c4441.poster.avif?t=1760645571\" width=620 height=313 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/ca8a79f05ddc2b131727d551023c4441.webm?t=1760645571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>感受极速度</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在多种游戏模式中称霸赛道。精准掌控每一次甩尾和飘逸，灵活躲避车流，把握最佳时机加速。每场比赛都是惊心动魄的生死追逐，一次失误可能就是满盘皆输。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/beb0e4e64d1139cdac23893dba71735c.poster.avif?t=1760645571\" width=620 height=313 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/beb0e4e64d1139cdac23893dba71735c.webm?t=1760645571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>超高速复古美学</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在电音合成器的动感节奏中漫游霓虹天际线，感受原汁原味的复古街机美学。《霓虹巅峰：超越极限》将80年代的赛博幻想融合现代感十足的竞速体验，让街机风格与极致速度在碰撞中共同狂飙。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/2a366c59f1f9ca12944526fa4533666c.poster.avif?t=1760645571\" width=620 height=313 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039250/extras/2a366c59f1f9ca12944526fa4533666c.webm?t=1760645571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成为都市传奇</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在全球排行榜上争夺冠军之名，把名字刻上荣耀之巅。成败在此一举，切记保持警觉。</p>",
